## DEC-007 — Sheet 3 topology fix: misplaced labels + missing pairs + 47 tie wires

**Date**: 2026-04-13 12:41

**Decision**: Fix Sheet 3 (`adrv9009_signals.sch`) so every FMC↔SOM pair
used by the design is correctly labeled and wire-tied, matching the
authoritative spreadsheet (`ADRV9009_UltraZed_EV_Pin_Mapping.xlsx`,
