correctness bug. Independent verification revealed:

1. The audit's CRIT-1 table was generated from stale `Text Notes`
   annotations on Sheet 3 (80 text notes referencing signal names from
   pre-V1 design states), not from the actual global label set. The
   audit conflated text notes with pin assignments. CRIT-1 and CRIT-1a
